{"tid":982251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"戇男冒聯合國官員　三星上將譯成「Samsung」","createTime":"2019-01-15T03:32:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T03:46:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18047919aea124dbba2e74988af471d4ffb9ca3a","tid":982251,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:32:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190115/photo/bkn-20190115065717039-0115_00952_001_01p.jpg?20190115072244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190115%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190115065717039-0115_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20190115072244&h=3812a2c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浙江農民余思高過去冒充聯合國，成立「聯合國維和部隊總司令部」，成員更遍布10多個省市，經常招搖撞騙。當中一名男子近日「申領」完有關證件後數天，隨即被警方拘捕，並發現證件內容錯漏百出，當中職銜「三星上將」竟譯成「Admiral Samsung」，事件引發網上笑彈。 <br />\n<br />\n據指，假證相信是來自一名來自新疆吉木薩爾的楊永亮，而證上則詳細盡列其個人資料，包括出生日期、籍貫、民族、部門、職務及職級。不過當細看英文的翻譯後便發現，用字錯得離譜，除了變成「三星」上將，籍貫中出現的「吉木薩爾」更錯寫成「Jiasar」。 <br />\n<br />\n不過更離譜的錯誤則出現出生日期一欄內，上面明明寫明「1971.6.12」，惟下面則寫有「October 23,1949」（1949年10月23日），事件被網民調侃指造證者失敗。而這名「三星上將」月初領證後不到數天，即被警方逮捕。 <br />\n<br />\n對於有人冒充「聯合國維和部隊總司令部」的事件並非首次，該「組織」估計至今已有數百名成員，遍及貴州、湖南、湖北等10多個城市。成員不但假借聯合國的名義招搖撞騙，部分人甚至到監獄提犯、到銀行存假鈔、坐車不付錢等，事件一度驚動聯合國發聲明澄清；創始人余思高早年因證據不足，只被檢方以「私刻公章」拘留15天。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190115/bkn-20190115065717039-0115_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190115%2Fbkn-20190115065717039-0115_00952_001.html&d=7Q0TnbiuGBwu1kYG%2F7S3uv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ccf56642\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190115/bkn-20190115065717039-0115_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"93db6af5b86135c5dd75514fb04cae85fac72811","tid":982251,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:37:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a10cdd871d2c2a35439b82ac1276c7751389b2c","tid":982251,"uid":224561,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:37:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88aVXG2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88aVXG2.gif&h=0dbd9a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5cfdcc701719f8efed0095304abd86bef3cb05","tid":982251,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:37:46.000Z","msg":"Admiral Sony is guilty"},{"pid":"64dd6852866a3ba94cf3f220acd48c114cc1f468","tid":982251,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:38:47.000Z","msg":"baidu translate fail"},{"pid":"f59c8f3ead301aaf94fc7b9c23865ff6abd414e3","tid":982251,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:39:37.000Z","msg":"個出生日期都唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc5345377ec86aa9833466abfb05764a7340228","tid":982251,"uid":171058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:46:24.000Z","msg":"又柒出國際，大陸L偷呃拐騙梗中一樣!"},{"pid":"e682182e936ef3f64773b94579d9ad5794c86ed4","tid":982251,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T03:46:51.000Z","msg":"這是正式錄用的上將嗎?"}]}